page.description: Dolt is a hybrid of a relational database and a version control system (specifically: MySQL and Git). One can run SQL queries, but also do version control and work on branches (both the database structure and the data are versioned).
KGT converts between various kinds of BNF-like syntaxes (BNF, ABNF, ISO-EBNF, RBNF, WSN) and creates railroad diagrams.
Tagref is a tool for managing labeled notes in comments and references to these notes. It ensures the references are valid:
Chcesz zrobić mi prezent, a nie wiesz, co można mi podarować? Poniżej aktualizowana stosunkowo często lista życzeń. Przedmioty mogą być używane, byle w dobrym stanie.
